1. How did NJ Transit provide visibility into its complex operations and performance?
solution : A. By creating a scorecard with dimensions similar to the Balanced Scorecard pillars, and making it available to stakeholders

2. What additional pillar did NJ Transit add to their scorecard?
solution : B. Safety and Security

3. Which Salesforce products did NJ Transit adopt to drive better performance?
solution : C. Service cloud and Chatter
